certbot-dns-infoblox (0.4.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Replaced infoblox-client dependency with minimal built-in WAPI client
    using requests directly against the Infoblox WAPI REST API.
  * Added Debian/Ubuntu packaging.
  * Added GitHub Actions CI/CD pipeline.
  * Migrated project metadata from setup.py/setup.cfg to pyproject.toml.

